John
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:short for John Hop, a cop, policeman (but SOED and AND derive from gendarme, cf. John Dunn).
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
